-- Hamworthy Gets $75 Million Order From Brazilian Shipyard Estaleio Promar
-- Benjamin Purvis
-- 2010-07-15T07:30:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/hamworthy-gets-50-million-pound-order-from-brazil-shipyard-estaleio-promar.html

          
          
             Hamworthy Plc was awarded a contract
worth around 50 million pounds from Brazilian shipyard Estaleio
Promar SA, the company said in a statement today.  
 The contract is for ship design and supply of cargo
handling systems for eight LPG carriers, Hamworthy said.  
          
          


  


        